    "description": "Field Tactics 是一款基于回合制的战术战争模拟器，其灵感来源于古代战争。设计你的独家阵型，利用各种战术，带领你的军队走向胜利。<br><br>你的目标是抓住敌人的指挥官，或者歼灭他们的军队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/fcddbc9333ebfce01e916ecc393e048d.poster.avif?t=1725312598\" width=600 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/fcddbc9333ebfce01e916ecc393e048d.webm?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/fcddbc9333ebfce01e916ecc393e048d.mp4?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >赛事类型</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>在线休闲：</strong>在不影响排名的情况下进行游戏，也是测试创新的战略和对战完美的对手的绝佳舞台。<br><br></li><li><strong>在线排名：</strong>考验你的能力，将你的名字刻在历史的长河中。使用你头脑库中的每一种策略，向成为大指挥官更进一步。<br><br></li><li><strong>本地联机：</strong>一个远离敌人窥视的机会。制定新的有趣的计划，或者只是与你的核心圈子成员之间的友好竞赛。<br><br></li><li><strong>人机对战：</strong>试验并解锁新的玩法，发掘新棋谱，不对核心圈子成员泄露任何“天机”。或者在你的游戏好友忙于其他事情时，帮助你提升棋艺并保持头脑清醒。<br><br></li><li><strong>征服：</strong>在这片土地上征战，在各种地形上证明自己的实力，并获得大指挥官的称号。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >棋子</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>步兵：</strong>战场上最常见的棋子。他们是勤劳的士兵，愿意为胜利牺牲自己的一切。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/d9f340cd9a6cab4d27801d85a0e1cb5a.poster.avif?t=1725312598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/d9f340cd9a6cab4d27801d85a0e1cb5a.webm?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/d9f340cd9a6cab4d27801d85a0e1cb5a.mp4?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>弓箭手：</strong>军队中重要的组成部分，他们监视着前线，捕杀越界的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/e47bec400380c9a60e6e6fa521644bf0.poster.avif?t=1725312598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/e47bec400380c9a60e6e6fa521644bf0.webm?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/e47bec400380c9a60e6e6fa521644bf0.mp4?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>战车：</strong>它们有可能成为最具破坏性的武器。一旦它们开始行动，就无法被阻止，并会抹平前进道路上的一切障碍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/2325ad18cc8e5a63889e79b93b415db6.poster.avif?t=1725312598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/2325ad18cc8e5a63889e79b93b415db6.webm?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/2325ad18cc8e5a63889e79b93b415db6.mp4?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>中尉：</strong>指挥官最忠诚的下属，他们最善于控制战斗流程，并可以创造出“星火燎原”的效果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/95f7f449c9c8dd56566fab11f1b21364.poster.avif?t=1725312598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/95f7f449c9c8dd56566fab11f1b21364.webm?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/95f7f449c9c8dd56566fab11f1b21364.mp4?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>指挥官：</strong>指挥官可以驰骋沙场，在任何时候都能扭转局势。但要小心，可能会因为潜入太深落入敌人的陷阱。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/c6a46822cb6cca9ab451dd750ef718b1.poster.avif?t=1725312598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/c6a46822cb6cca9ab451dd750ef718b1.webm?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204570/extras/c6a46822cb6cca9ab451dd750ef718b1.mp4?t=1725312598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
